  <fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KS.xml" title="section-retraction pair" addr="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1,b_2\in  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}=s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, we must show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=b_2]]></fr:tex>. We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> by assumption, and thus <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b_1=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_1\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=r{\mathopen {}\left (s{\mathopen {}\left (b_2\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}=b_2]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
